      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUNLIKE SKIPPY (3) rocketed out of the boxes with a sizzling early split and led throughout to score when a 2.25 lengths winner (30.19) over 500m at this track. Can continue on his winning ways. FABULOUS IMAGE (4) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Ballycleary Bono (30.47) in an A6. Has the pace to be prominent. Expecting another good run. LAMORNA LILL MOO (5) finds it hard to win. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (30.63) at this track. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings nine times from 13 starts. Bold showing expected. COOLEMORE SOUTH (6) is a course and distance winner worth keeping in mind.",
